    CardExchangeController

    Controller
    This controller class will controls the main user interface.
    GameparametersDialogController
    This class contains the methods that are used to get the no of players based on the user selection and their characters and the choosen map.
    LoadgameController
    This class loads the map into game window panel.
    MapEditorController
    This class displays the text area for the user to edit the map.
    NewMapController
    This NewMapController class is responsible for controlling the newmap window This class creates the Textarea to construct the newmap and saves the map if the map is valid.
    PhaseViewController
    This class controls the phase view window.
    PlayersDominationViewController
    This controller is controls the players domination view window This controller responsible for displaying the actions happening in the background of the game.
